node.text:
Another one! Honored to win the @FedEx Ground @NFL Player of the Year for the second straight year. For winning, FedEx will donate $20K to @DirectRelief in my name. The donation will help deliver emergency medical backpacks in the Nashville community. 👍

& Thank you to the best fans in the NFL (Titans) & everyone else who voted ! 🙏🏾
